<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/7010322-jenny">Jenny</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes, there are three &quot;books&quot; and this one contains only the first two. In Japan, the two first books were published in 2009 on the same date while the<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes, there are three "books" and this one contains only the first two. In Japan, the two first books were published in 2009 on the same date while the third book was published in 2010. Vintage has decided to publish them in the same constellation.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
