<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/14114603-elleh-rachelle">Elleh Rachelle</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If I were you I wouldn&apos;t think of skipping any pages, there is no repeats however the chapters are linked according to the three characters Aomame, Te<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If I were you I wouldn't think of skipping any pages, there is no repeats however the chapters are linked according to the three characters Aomame, Tengo and Ushikawa. So if you skip the pages or chapters, you might not get the actual story, however there are something that you can ignore like the parts or sections where the author has borrowed stories from others work, of course giving full credit. <br />This book is my best read I can say this year, unless another book wins me.☺☺☺<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
